Time Arrival City Train No. Trains to & from Xian Xi’an, as a historical and cultural ancient capital of China, attracts numerous tourists every year. To help tourists plan a great trip to Xi’an, China Highlights is pleased to provide you with the train schedule for Xi’an Railway Station and Xi’an Bei Railway Station, helping you get well prepared beforehand. We sincerely hope that this information is useful for your trip. Xi’an is the transport hub of northwest China and many trains run through it. China Highlights is pleased to provide the Xi’an train schedule for passengers going to Xi’an.
